[
    {
        "text": "Here's how to make a table",
        "start": 0.84,
        "duration": 1.33
    },
    {
        "text": "in Microsoft Excel.",
        "start": 2.17,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "A table is a specific\nset of rows and columns",
        "start": 3.94,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "that you can apply functions to",
        "start": 6.61,
        "duration": 1.63
    },
    {
        "text": "such as adding filters, formatting,",
        "start": 8.24,
        "duration": 2.291
    },
    {
        "text": "or creating graphs.",
        "start": 10.531,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's turn our buying report",
        "start": 12.431,
        "duration": 1.469
    },
    {
        "text": "for our fashion startup into a table.",
        "start": 13.9,
        "duration": 2.97
    },
    {
        "text": "First, highlight the cells",
        "start": 16.87,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "you want to add to your table,",
        "start": 18.52,
        "duration": 1.558
    },
    {
        "text": "click on \"Insert,\" then click on \"Table.\"",
        "start": 20.078,
        "duration": 2.782
    },
    {
        "text": "If your cells include headings,",
        "start": 22.86,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "check the \"My table has headers\" box,",
        "start": 24.54,
        "duration": 3.308
    },
    {
        "text": "then click \"OK.\"",
        "start": 27.848,
        "duration": 1.625
    },
    {
        "text": "Your cells will now be\nturned into a table.",
        "start": 29.473,
        "duration": 2.38
    },
    {
        "text": "On the top-right corner of the screen",
        "start": 34.33,
        "duration": 1.73
    },
    {
        "text": "under the \"Table\" section,",
        "start": 36.06,
        "duration": 1.45
    },
    {
        "text": "you'll see a series of colored designs.",
        "start": 37.51,
        "duration": 2.59
    },
    {
        "text": "Choose the one you like,",
        "start": 40.1,
        "duration": 1.225
    },
    {
        "text": "and you'll see your table change.",
        "start": 41.325,
        "duration": 2.158
    },
    {
        "text": "You can expand the size of your table",
        "start": 45.85,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "by amending the number\nof columns or rows in it.",
        "start": 47.65,
        "duration": 3.02
    },
    {
        "text": "To do this, hover your cursor",
        "start": 50.67,
        "duration": 1.67
    },
    {
        "text": "over the bottom-right corner of the table",
        "start": 52.34,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "and click and drag the\nblack-arrowed square",
        "start": 54.3,
        "duration": 2.79
    },
    {
        "text": "across the columns or rows",
        "start": 57.09,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "you want to be added to your table.",
        "start": 58.41,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "The sort and filter features on tables",
        "start": 60.93,
        "duration": 2.26
    },
    {
        "text": "help to organize your data.",
        "start": 63.19,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Click on the drop-down arrow",
        "start": 65.39,
        "duration": 1.483
    },
    {
        "text": "next to one of the headings.",
        "start": 66.873,
        "duration": 1.677
    },
    {
        "text": "A pop-up will appear.",
        "start": 68.55,
        "duration": 1.303
    },
    {
        "text": "Next to \"Sort,\" click on \"Ascending.\"",
        "start": 71.44,
        "duration": 2.63
    },
    {
        "text": "The table will now be arranged",
        "start": 74.07,
        "duration": 1.48
    },
    {
        "text": "in ascending order of retail prices.",
        "start": 75.55,
        "duration": 2.323
    },
    {
        "text": "Now use the filter function",
        "start": 78.91,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "by unchecking one of these boxes.",
        "start": 80.27,
        "duration": 2.29
    },
    {
        "text": "This will hide all the items on the table",
        "start": 82.56,
        "duration": 1.966
    },
    {
        "text": "that are $182.50.",
        "start": 84.526,
        "duration": 3.233
    }
]